programs.name: GYM: 5 DAY PPL Upper/Lower
programs.description: The PPL Upper/Lower is Mike's favourite split of 2025. It combines the infamous PPL split with an added upper and lower day allowing for all muscle groups to be trained twice per week. This is for intermediate - advanced lifters who are focused on building strength, size and hitting all muscle groups equally. A great opportunity to increase weights lifted and hit PR's with the reduced rep ranges and increased rest periods. *This is only available as a 5 day option.
